MOLDAVITE RINGS 💚 from @moonlightjewelsco

$80 usd 💫 available in sizes 4-10

Free tracked shipping to Canada and USA • Worldwide shipping also available 

Moldavite is a kind of green volcanic glass called Tektite formed from a meteorite impact. It's said to have fallen from space about 15 million years ago.

Moldavite is great for meditation and is said to clear blockages, helps aid in spiritual transformation, healing and evolution.

node.text:
Tag a friend who needs this beautiful piece from @thewitchdoctorrx 🔮🌈

Sun Catchers and Light Catchers ☀️ have been used all across the globe for centuries to harness the magic, love & light that this beautiful star 🌟has to offer. Although, the moon 🌙 is never seen with its horns facing down in nature, the only way it would be scientifically possible is for the sun and the moon to be extremely close together. This inspired the design of the Selene Light Catcher, where the sun and moon work together to illuminate our lives. 

Head over to  the Apothecary at www.thewitchdoctorrx.com, where they’re always utilizing science ⚗️🔬and the craft to come up with new brews 💫💕
